org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id WHERE issues.author_id = 3 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL ORDER BY issues.id DESC LIMIT 1
